- addSharer
- toggleSharer
- getSharerInfoById, getSharerInfoByCode
    gives complete info on a single sharerer, all their clicks (with info), and actions (with info)
- getAllSharers
    gives sharer id, code link, clicks count, actions count, and enabled only
- getActionTypes
